	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hopefully I'll finish this game off then I'll write a post up on what does what online somewhere, also, wow,yeah, I haven't published anything on my blog in a while! I should probably make sure to update more often next year!<br /><br />GBDK is what has led me down towards ASM, sooo, yeah, let's see how it goes.<br /><br />Regarding the random generator, I'm just taking a value, multiplying by 13, adding 1 then sotring that as the next rand.<br /><br />But I'm only updating that random generator when I need to. So, it's not per frame or anything, has a pattern of sorts, yet seems to be pretty random for the genreated levels at least so far. There's some obvious elements inside each level but I'll be making each world with a different stlye of generation, all using the same PRNG though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
